Binding: initialize_cruise
Title: Initialize Cruise Project
Subtitle: Select Ship and Deployments. More can be added later!

Parameter: select_ship
Widget:SelectInput
Label: Select Ship
Fields: RCS, CC
Postion: left

Parameter: neuston
Widget: CheckboxInput
Label: Neuston Tow
Default: On

Parameter: meter
Widget: CheckboxInput
Label: Meter Net
Default: On

Parameter: ctd
Widget: CheckboxInput
Label: Hydrocast and/or Free CTD
Default: On

Parameter: secchi
Widget: CheckboxInput
Label: Secchi Disk
Default: Off

Parameter: niskins_on_wire
Widget: CheckboxInput
Label: Niskins on the Wire
Default: Off
Position: right

Parameter: free_ctd
Widget: CheckboxInput
Label: Free CTDs only (no bottles)
Default: Off
Position: right

Parameter: obs
Widget: CheckboxInput
Label: Obs Data (Creates separate summary sheet)
Default: Off
Position: right

